Subject: [PATCH 0373/1072] ENGR00274768-1 ARM: imx6q: update gint bit
 definitions of IOMUXC_GPR1

git://git.freescale.com/imx/linux-2.6-imx.git imx_3.10.17_1.0.0_beta
commit 326b5b455ec21a40772672379e79282515185366

Need to use IOMUXC_GPR1_GINT bit for cpuidle driver, so update this
bit's definitions.

Signed-off-by: Anson Huang <b20788@freescale.com>
Signed-off-by: Hongbo Zhong <hongbo.zhong@windriver.com>
